  - 749
By: Sri Ramakrishna
---
Sometimes God acts as the magnet and the devotee as the needle. God
attracts the devotee to Himself. Again, sometimes the devotee acts as
the magnet and God as the needle. Such is the attraction of the
devotee that God comes to him, unable to resist his love.
